Package org.coliper.ibean.proxy

Class IBeanContext<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.coliper.ibean.proxy.IBeanContext<T>
  • public class IBeanContext<T>
extends Object
    IBeanContext is provided to ExtensionHandlers to provide them information about the context of a IBean method call. Only used in ExtensionHandler context, for example in ExtensionHandler.handleExtendedInterfaceCall(IBeanContext, IBeanFieldAccess, Object, java.lang.reflect.Method, Object[])
